These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, coral, green
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, monopoly, snooker
4 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, chinchilla, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, jet-ski, taxi, boat
 1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 2. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 5. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 6. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes coral##1
10. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
11. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
12. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
13. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
14. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |       3       |        4        |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | juice        | hot-chocolate | almond-milk     |
| Color          | blue    | mauve  | coral     | green          |
| Game           | bridge | monopoly     | chess    | snooker |
| Pet   | rabbit     | mouse    | chinchilla       | ferret          |
| Transport         | snowmobile  | taxi | jet-ski       | boat         |

