.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, tram, car
There 4 different types of food: apple, carrot, cucumber, radish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, marigold, balloon-flower
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, goldfish, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, may, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 6. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
11. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the owner of the lizard is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who's birthday is in july##2
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
14. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |      2      |      3       |      4       |
| Transport   | airplane        | tram    | car        | bike         |
| Food       | cucumber   | carrot      | radish       | apple        |
| Flower      | rose | marigold | balloon-flower  | amaryllis |
| Pet        | rat  | bird   | lizard   | goldfish     |
| Birthday      | august | july    | may | march       |

