The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, funk, soul
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, montecristo, game, aristoff
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
 6. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the montecristo-smoker##5
 7. the person who growsiris is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who growsorchid##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the fan of country##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
11. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing go##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
13. the fan of funk is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |     4     |
