.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-4::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, chess, poker
There 4 different types of food: mango, cherry, lettuce, grapes
4 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, dog, chinchilla
There are 4 different nationalities: british, japanese, spanish, turkish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, milk, almond-milk
 1. the person eating mango is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person playing backgammon##2
 2. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the person eating grapes is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 9. the person playing chess is the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the spanish is the person eating lettuce##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
12. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
13. the owner of the snake is between the person playing backgammon and the owner of the dog##2
14. the person drinking juice is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Game           | backgammon | monopoly | poker | chess |
| Food   | lettuce     | mango   | cherry  | grapes   |
| Pet   | lizard       | snake  | dog       | chinchilla        |
| Nationality   | spanish    | british  | turkish      | japanese     |
| Beverage         | juice | milk | almond-milk     | lemonade     |

