 1. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 6. the person driving the ship is the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the car##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
13. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
14. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
