 1. the person playing go is on the right of the fisherman##1
 2. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 3. the electrician is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 4. the owner of the snake is the electrician##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the lizard and the electrician##2
 7. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 9. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
10. the person eating cherry is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing bridge##1
12. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating peas##1
13. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
14. the person who's sport is surfing is the electrician##1
15. the person playing go is in an even position##4
16. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3

