The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, amaryllis, aconite
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, police-officer, writer, social-worker
 1. the spanish is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 2. the person who growsaconite is between the person who growsorchid and the social-worker##2
